          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ul>
            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Device</div>Spy radio set            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Purpose</div>Mid- to long range agent communication            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Manufacturer</div>Telefunken, Hannover (Germany)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Model</div>M2B            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Successor</div><a href="../esk52">ESK-52</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Frequency</div>3-16 MHz            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Power</div>Mains or battery            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Mains</div>90-140V and 190-250V <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Alternating Current">AC</span>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Battery</div>6V <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Direct Current">DC</span>          </ul>
</font></td></tr></table>        <a name=spec_tx></a>
